759
00:45:46,286 --> 00:45:48,121
Maybe it's changing.

760
00:45:48,204 --> 00:45:49,789
What is?

761
00:45:50,665 --> 00:45:53,668
The city, the way things work or don't.

762
00:45:56,379 --> 00:45:57,607
Maybe we're turning a corner here

763
00:45:57,631 --> 00:46:00,383
and it's not gonna be so
unbelievably fucked up any more.

764
00:46:02,886 --> 00:46:04,512
To carcetti.

765
00:46:05,722 --> 00:46:07,223
And us.

766
