787
00:47:27,387 --> 00:47:28,722
Randy?

788
00:47:29,597 --> 00:47:31,474
"According to the text..."?

789
00:47:31,558 --> 00:47:34,686
"According to the text."

790
00:47:34,769 --> 00:47:35,812
That's good.

791
00:47:35,895 --> 00:47:38,690
And how do we end the answer?

792
00:47:38,773 --> 00:47:40,400
Quanice?

793
00:47:40,483 --> 00:47:42,610
Come on. I know you know this.

794
00:47:47,115 --> 00:47:51,369
"The above-stated facts have
led me to conclude that..."

795
00:47:51,453 --> 00:47:52,704
Right?

796
00:47:52,787 --> 00:47:55,373
Ok. So, let's try to read
the third paragraph.

797
00:47:55,457 --> 00:47:59,836
I'll start it. "Pythias makes a final plea
to the tyrant dionysius

798
00:47:59,919 --> 00:48:04,758
"to return to his home one last..."
Calvin, pick it up.

799
00:48:04,841 --> 00:48:08,386
"To return to his home one last time
before his punishment.

800
00:48:08,470 --> 00:48:12,223
"He denies the request
until Damon inter..."

801
00:48:13,558 --> 00:48:14,726
Intercedes.

802
00:48:17,604 --> 00:48:20,440
"And offers his own life
until pythias returns."

803
00:48:20,523 --> 00:48:24,652
Good. Who wants to guess
what "intercedes" means?

804
00:48:32,494 --> 00:48:33,828
