808
00:48:46,883 --> 00:48:48,676
According to the text...

809
00:48:48,760 --> 00:48:51,429
Everybody's safe in the end, right?

810
00:48:53,598 --> 00:48:55,475
Ok. Let's think this through.

811
00:48:55,558 --> 00:48:57,352
"According to the text,

812
00:48:57,435 --> 00:49:00,230
"Damon offers his own life
on behalf of pythias

813
00:49:00,313 --> 00:49:02,440
"so that he can return home
one last time.

814
00:49:02,524 --> 00:49:05,235
"The above-stated facts
have led me to conclude

815
00:49:05,318 --> 00:49:09,322
