842
00:50:48,755 --> 00:50:51,216
I mean, he's carcetti's man, but...

843
00:50:52,508 --> 00:50:54,010
Daniels?

844
00:50:58,014 --> 00:51:01,476
Long time for you to make major,
but this was quick enough.

845
00:51:01,559 --> 00:51:03,561
Yeah, who's your new rabbi, huh?

846
00:51:03,645 --> 00:51:05,355
Colonel.

847
00:51:05,438 --> 00:51:09,984
So, they didn't know the salad fork from
